<br>
We like to think that most people who come the boards are adults or can at least behave as one.  A little bit of adult content will be allowed but do not go overboard.<br>
<br>
Our board is not a democracy.  If something gets posted in any section of our board that we do not find acceptable, it will be edited or removed.  A post will be in place of it stating you have been warned and can lead to being banned for repeated offenders.  Guildies usually are not banned from the board, however their posts get clipped or disappear frequently too.<br>
<br>
We do not tolerate outright flames or threats, and if a topic boils down to a pissing contest between a few people, the posts will disappear, regardless of the relevance of the original topic.  We are not kindergarten teachers, please don’t make us act like them.<br>
